## .NET gitignore — standard for ASP.NET Core projects

# Build output
[Bb]in/
[Oo]bj/
[Oo]ut/
[Ll]og/
[Ll]ogs/

# Visual Studio / Rider
.vs/
.idea/
*.user
*.suo
*.userosscache
*.sln.docstates

# NuGet
*.nupkg
*.snupkg
**/[Pp]ackages/
!**/[Pp]ackages/build/
*.nuget.props
*.nuget.targets
project.lock.json
project.fragment.lock.json
artifacts/

# Publish output
**/publish/
**/PublishProfiles/

# Test results
[Tt]est[Rr]esult*/
[Bb]uild[Ll]og.*
*.trx
*.coverage
*.coveragexml
coverage*/

# MSBuild crash logs
MSBuildCrashLogs/

# dotnet tool manifests (local, not committed)
.dotnet/

# Docker build context exclusions (via .dockerignore preferred)
# but keep here as safety net
*.env
*.env.*
!*.env.example
secrets/

# OS junk
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
